=head1 PURPOSE

Test L<Type::Params> positional parameters, a la the example in the
documentation:

   sub nth_root
   {
      state $check = compile( Num, Num );
      my ($x, $n) = $check->(@_);
      
      return $x ** (1 / $n);
   }

